757
01:04:53,180 --> 01:04:54,520
<i>I confessed today</i>

758
01:04:55,141 --> 01:04:56,311
<i>that I killed someone,</i>

759
01:04:56,392 --> 01:04:58,442
<i>and I threatened
to kill him too if need be.</i>

760
01:04:59,353 --> 01:05:01,443
What? What is it?

761
01:05:01,522 --> 01:05:03,482
-What did you do to Mr. Lee Jingeun?
-What?

762
01:05:04,025 --> 01:05:06,525
<i>Someone came by.
I think they said they were family.</i>

763
01:05:07,278 --> 01:05:08,818
<i>If we say no…</i>

764
01:05:08,905 --> 01:05:10,355
<i>She'll report us to the police.</i>

765
01:05:10,448 --> 01:05:12,158
-Mom, where are you going?
-Just go, both of you!

766
01:05:12,241 --> 01:05:15,041
<i>Anyone that knows about the incident
or gets in the way of Dahyun,</i>

767
01:05:15,119 --> 01:05:17,119
<i>I'll get rid of them.</i>

768
01:05:23,127 --> 01:05:25,127
Translated by [Ji-young Hwang]
